ns0:review-result.project-name: Code Review Plugin for TIBCO BusinessWorks - IT - Demo project

ns1:infos.ns1:name: Nested loops
ns1:infos.ns1:description: Nested loops should be avoided for performance reason.
ns1:infos.ns1:descriptionHTML: Nested loops should be avoided for performance reason.
ns1:infos.ns1:correctionHTML: When a mapper is inside a loop, it can be replaced by a simple mapper with XSLT 'for-each' construct.

ns1:infos.ns1:name: Critical Section on JobSharedVariable
ns1:infos.ns1:description: Critical Section around JobSharedVariable is useless
ns1:infos.ns1:descriptionHTML: Critical Section around JobSharedVariable is useless since a JobSharedVariable is related to a single job.

ns1:infos.ns1:name: Critical Section on single SharedVariable
ns1:infos.ns1:descriptionHTML: Critical Section on a single SharedVariable access is useless, SharedVariable activities are thread-safe and critical section should only be used for consistency matters.

ns1:infos.ns1:name: Get JMS Queue Message Uses
ns1:infos.ns1:descriptionHTML: Get JMS Queue Message Uses activity is expensive for EMS server.

ns1:infos.ns1:name: JMS Selector
ns1:infos.ns1:descriptionHTML: JMS Selector can slow down EMS server throughput and increase CPU load

ns1:infos.ns1:name: JMS Synchronous activities
ns1:infos.ns1:descriptionHTML: JMS Synchronous activities are inefficient for scalability.

ns1:infos.ns1:name: Connection configuration hardcoded
ns1:infos.ns1:description: All fields of a connection should be parameterized with Global Variables.
ns1:infos.ns1:descriptionHTML: All fields of a connection should be parameterized with Global Variables.

ns1:infos.ns1:name: Default targetNameSpace in schema definition
ns1:infos.ns1:description: The targetNameSpace of the XML Schema Definition (XSD) starts with 'http://www.tibco.com'. It is most likely the default value set by the Designer. A good targetNameSpace should be customized with a mnemonic name such as 'http://company.com/category/feature.xsd'.
ns1:infos.ns1:descriptionHTML:
The targetNameSpace of the XSD starts with http://www.tibco.com
It is most likely the default value set by the Designer.
ns1:infos.ns1:correctionHTML: A good targetNameSpace should be customized with a mnemonic name such as http://company.com/category/feature.xsd.

ns1:infos.ns1:name: Colors in Transition
ns1:infos.ns1:description: Colors in Transition reduce the readibility of the process in the debugger and can lead to misunderstanding of the process logic.
ns1:infos.ns1:descriptionHTML: Colors in Transition reduce the readibility of the process in the debugger and can lead to misunderstanding of the process logic.

ns1:infos.ns1:name: No out Transition
ns1:infos.ns1:description: When an activity has no transition to another activity, the behaviour of the process at runtime might become undefined. All activities must have at least one successor in the process graph, except the End activity.
ns1:infos.ns1:descriptionHTML:
When an activity has no transition to another activity, the behaviour of the process at runtime might become undefined.
All activities must have at least one successor in the process graph, except the End activity.
ns1:infos.ns1:correctionHTML: Simply add a transition from the concerned activity to another activity or to the End activity.

ns1:infos.ns1:name: No otherwise Transition
ns1:infos.ns1:description: When an activity has transitions with condition(s), the Otherwise transition is mandatory.
ns1:infos.ns1:descriptionHTML: When an activity has transitions with condition(s), the Otherwise transition is mandatory.
ns1:infos.ns1:correctionHTML: Simply add an Otherwise transition from the concerned activity to another activity or to the End activity.
